ZH: 我们需要分组来完成这个任务。
EN: We need to divide into groups to complete this task.

ZH: 我们可以将学生分成几个分组。
EN: We can divide the students into a few groups.

ZH: 分组比独自工作更加高效。
EN: Working in groups is more efficient than working alone.

ZH: 请将你们分组为四人一组。
EN: Please divide yourselves into groups of four.

ZH: 这个项目需要进行合适的分组。
EN: This project requires the right division of groups.

ZH: 我们将分组进行比赛。
EN: We will divide into groups for the competition.

ZH: 他们已经分组完成任务了。
EN: They have already divided into groups to complete the task.

ZH: 我们希望能够分组进行研究。
EN: We hope to be able to group for research.

